{
  "stem": "1550.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kaplan from Boston who gave this affidavit for me-- only for me, not for my parents because there was a difficulty with my parents.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As you know, the United States has a quota-- had a quota system.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The quota system is based on the place where you are born.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now I was born in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother was born in Austria.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father, by accident, was born in what is now Poland, although he hated the Polish Jews so much.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He could never forget that he was born in Poland himself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, that was-- he could never get over-- all his life he, who had hated the Polish Jews so much, he was himself a Polish Jew, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But it was a pure accident because his family is from Hungary, but his grandfather at one time was residing for a short time there, so that's how he was born in Poland.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the problem was because he was born in Poland, he, he fell under the Polish quota.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Polish quota was over-fulfilled, fulfilled for about 10 years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You see what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Polish quota for to go to the United States was very small.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Austrian quota, which was added to the German quota, was about 30,000 people a year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I could-- if I have an affadavit, I could go within a few months or my mother also.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my mother wouldn't go without my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to go somewhere else, but there was no-- no-- there was no place to go, absolutely no place to go.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we tried other things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a question of going with a kinder transport to England, but I was a little bit too old, I think, for that.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
